  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网执行器控制器画一个状态图。这个控制器有两种基本运行状态：静止和运动，另外还要考虑一个故障状态——崩溃。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到您提到了MQTT Broker，这个Broker在状态转换中扮演什么角色？是作为状态本身，还是作为外部通信节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "MQTT Broker是外部通信节点。控制器启动后先进入静止状态，同时向Broker上报状态；静止和运动之间可以双向切换；运动过程中如果发生异常就进入崩溃状态，崩溃后也需要通知Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我梳理一下：控制器起始于静止状态，静止和运动互相转换，运动可能转入崩溃，静止和崩溃都要连接Broker上报。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但还要补充一点：控制器初始状态就是静止，所以起点直接连到静止，不需要额外的起始节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Still"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2来绘制。控制器作为起点连接到静止状态，静止分出两条线：一条到Broker，一条到运动。运动再连回静止，同时引出崩溃状态，崩溃也连到Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，静止到Broker的箭头方向反了。应该是静止状态指向Broker，表示上报，不是Broker指向静止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在静止和崩溃都正确指向MQTT Broker。整个状态流转：控制器→静止↔运动，运动→崩溃，静止→Broker，崩溃→Broker。您确认这样可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
